INSERT INTO `topic_reply` VALUES ('5be2a7d7646a05745b7b95fe', '5be29f7c21d75b74609f4fbf', '2018111306343304716358894956', '<div class=\"markdown-text\"><p>图文并茂，文章写的不错\n运营商劫持估计换https也不太行，有些恶心的，直接用iframe包住你的网页，它该显示照样显示，那群人为了赚钱野路子贼多。</p>\n</div>', null, '2018-11-07 08:52:39.415000', '2018-11-07 08:52:39.415000', '0');
INSERT INTO `topic_reply` VALUES ('5be2b2c4646a05745b7b967c', '5be29f7c21d75b74609f4fbf', '5bda8a7793f8d64f74b012ae', '<div class=\"markdown-text\"><p><a href=\"/user/zy445566\">@zy445566</a> 运营商劫持 https 可以解决的。</p>\n<p>运营商并不能在 https 的原文里添加任何信息，加了客户端就解不开了。</p>\n</div>', '5be2a7d7646a05745b7b95fe', '2018-11-07 09:39:16.291000', '2018-11-07 09:39:16.291000', '0');
INSERT INTO `topic_reply` VALUES ('5be2bd3121d75b74609f516d', '5be29f7c21d75b74609f4fbf', '2018111306344623291731237834', '<div class=\"markdown-text\"><p>对于访问量日IP没超过1万的网站来说，用caddy就够了，支持<strong>免费自动申请通配符https证书</strong>，配置非常简单。</p>\n<pre class=\"prettyprint\"><code>sudo yum update\nsudo yum install epel-release\nsudo yum install caddy\nsudo systemctl enable --now caddy.service\n\nvi &#x2F;etc&#x2F;caddy&#x2F;Caddyfile\n</code></pre><p>粘贴以下代码到<code>/etc/caddy/Caddyfile</code>中</p>\n<pre class=\"prettyprint\"><code>focalhot.com, www.focalhot.com {\n    redir 301 {\n      if {host} starts_with focalhot.com\n         &#x2F; https:&#x2F;&#x2F;www.focalhot.com{uri}\n    }\n    proxy &#x2F; 127.0.0.1:8080 {\n      transparent\n    }\n    gzip\n    tls focalhot@foxmail.com\n}\n</code></pre><p>重启caddy服务</p>\n<pre class=\"prettyprint\"><code>sudo systemctl restart caddy\n</code></pre></div>', null, '2018-11-07 10:23:45.090000', '2018-11-07 10:23:45.090000', '0');
